<H2>Keyboard shortcuts and controls</H2>
Keyboard shortcuts are a great way to speed up your work.
Look for them when you use menu commands, and try
to remember them for next time you use the commands.<P>


<H3>Standard shortcuts</A></H3>

<TABLE>

<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Ctrl+N</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Opens the new map dialog.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Ctrl+O</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Opens an exsisting map.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Ctrl+S</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Saves the current map.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Ctrl+X</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Cut selected tiles
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Ctrl+C</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Copy selected tiles
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Ctrl+V</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Paste the copied or cut tiles in the selected region.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Ctrl+A</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Selects the entire map.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Ctrl+M</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Opens the map properties dialog.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Ctrl+G</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Opens the game modes dialog.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Ctrl+L</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Opens the server dialog box.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Alt+F4</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Quits Gardener.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>F1</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Shows the online help documentation.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>F11</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Maximizes the window.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Del</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Deletes the current selection of tiles.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>T</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Switches to the terrain palette.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>O</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Switches to the object palette.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>E</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Switched to the event palette.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>1</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Changes current tool to pointer tool.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>2</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Changes current tool to fill tool.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>3</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Changes current tool to select tool.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>4</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Changes current tool to rectangle tool.
</FONT></TD></TR>
</TABLE>

<H3><A NAME="formatting">Controls</A></H3>

These are other misc controls which are good to know when editing VTank maps.<P>

<TABLE>

<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Shift+Scroll</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Allows the user to adjust the global height variable. 0 is the default and drivable hieght.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Left Mouse Button</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 Does different things depending open which tool is selected. In general it is used to select terrains, objects, and event from the selector and place them on the canvas.
</FONT></TD></TR>



<TR><TD WIDTH=30>
<TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=158>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
<B>Right Mouse Button</B>
</FONT></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP>
<FONT FACE="Arial, Lucida, Helvetica">
 While using the pointer tool, allows the user to place collision, which makes it so tanks won't be able to drive through that tile.
</FONT></TD></TR>

</TABLE>

